Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.79,0:01:37.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,累死了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.74,0:01:39.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为一直被监视着
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.99,0:01:42.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是叫老胡和兰芳吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.34,0:01:42.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.82,0:01:44.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,少主在哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.37,0:01:50.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他不在呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.55,0:01:52.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难道又失踪了？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.09,0:01:57.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的 一不注意就消失了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.25,0:02:00.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,少主
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.64,0:02:02.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,您去哪里了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.31,0:02:05.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又倒在路边的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.71,0:02:07.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,耳根清净了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.58,0:02:09.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们走
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.15,0:02:11.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.09,0:02:15.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,少主
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.51,0:02:17.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在哪
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.95,0:02:29.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个国家 有点不对劲
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.96,0:02:32.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(960,950)\fn方正大标宋_GBK\fs135\fsp12\blur6\bord5\1c&H00&\3c&HFFFFFFFF&}战友的足迹
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.19,0:02:46.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是我 来探望了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.19,0:02:49.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.31,0:02:51.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是大佐给的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.87,0:02:56.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哟 抽烟的大哥
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.84,0:02:58.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么样 赢过一回吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.31,0:03:00.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,完全赢不了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.53,0:03:02.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,话说 这个游戏太无聊了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.06,0:03:06.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我说 半夜的话可以去砍人吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.45,0:03:07.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么可以呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.82,0:03:11.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么 至少把霍克爱大姐带来
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.12,0:03:14.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 我回头和大姐说一声
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.38,0:03:19.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要监视他到什么时候？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.26,0:03:21.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大佐说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.66,0:03:25.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把你们卷进这么危险的任务 真是对不住
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.57,0:03:28.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,军务方面不用担心
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.68,0:03:30.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,算你是因病请假
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.71,0:03:35.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 如果被一般市民或我们的军队相关人员发现的话
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.23,0:03:37.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别想简单了事
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.39,0:03:39.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是这么说的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.47,0:03:43.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有没有前途一片光明的话题？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.66,0:03:45.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.89,0:03:46.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.24,0:03:49.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我交上女朋友了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.09,0:03:53.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,搬家遇见麻烦的时候 她对我很温柔
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.08,0:03:56.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是 超好的女孩
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.47,0:03:58.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果把那个女的砍了会不会很有趣
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.94,0:04:01.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,给我回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.87,0:04:06.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 不要紧吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.68,0:04:08.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,饭
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.62,0:04:10.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是饿倒的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.41,0:04:12.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是哪里人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.55,0:04:15.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么 从清国来的？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.38,0:04:18.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么从那大老远的地方跑过来
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.44,0:04:20.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,话说 你的入国许可证呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.10,0:04:25.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让开 让开
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.43,0:04:27.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,非法入国者要通过了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.08,0:04:29.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,少主
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.40,0:04:30.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在哪
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.17,0:04:32.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,倒在路边了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.84,0:04:34.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,绝对饿倒在路边了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.15,0:04:38.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么 我们就先去军部露个脸
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.13,0:04:39.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.62,0:04:44.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么 我就先去休斯家打个招呼吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.31,0:04:48.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想早点看看克蕾西亚和艾莉西亚
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.50,0:04:51.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,知道了 我们马上就过去
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.52,0:04:52.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么 过会见
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.12,0:05:02.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在那之后 休斯中佐有没有替我们收集贤者之石的情报呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.40,0:05:05.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且被大总统禁止了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.19,0:05:10.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,首先把我们入手的情报告诉他吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.60,0:05:12.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人造人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.13,0:05:13.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.77,0:05:17.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,中佐应该在军法会议所吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.67,0:05:20.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是那边
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.89,0:05:39.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢丝卡
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.43,0:05:41.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢丝卡
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.93,0:05:42.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.91,0:05:45.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你拿着那边的钥匙吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.49,0:05:46.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.86,0:05:49.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那 那个 是三号吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.33,0:05:51.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我用过后就这么放着没收拾
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.08,0:05:55.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没关系 我只是去拿需要的文件
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.43,0:05:56.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的不行
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.91,0:05:59.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我立刻去收拾 请稍等
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.11,0:06:04.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么我等会来拿 麻烦你快点哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.50,0:06:06.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.72,0:06:23.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个 大佐
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.82,0:06:24.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,马斯坦古大佐？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.79,0:06:32.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我睡了几分钟
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.22,0:06:34.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大约10分钟
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.23,0:06:40.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,离军队会议没多少时间了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.79,0:06:44.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个 也许是我多事
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.36,0:06:47.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,您还是不要太逞强多休息一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.03,0:06:49.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 我还会再来的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.85,0:06:55.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,刚才的是马斯坦古大佐？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.44,0:07:00.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,早 早上好 佛卡大尉
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.59,0:07:02.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,早上好 谢丝卡
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.02,0:07:05.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,话说 为什么大佐会在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.68,0:07:07.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个 那个
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.23,0:07:09.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,书库也开着
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.93,0:07:12.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起 其实那个
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.83,0:07:15.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,反正是被大佐强行要求的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.58,0:07:17.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我就当没看见好了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.68,0:07:20.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太感谢你了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.79,0:07:24.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,话说回来 大佐在调查什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.61,0:07:25.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你知道吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.80,0:07:29.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也不知道详细情况
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.35,0:07:33.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大佐问我有没有第五研究所的相关资料
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.21,0:07:37.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,另外 休斯准将的事件
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.15,0:07:44.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是准将介绍我到这里工作的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.67,0:07:46.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,的确如此
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.34,0:07:51.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天也有一堆工作
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.08,0:07:54.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拜托了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.96,0:07:56.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.77,0:08:14.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,早上好 谢丝卡
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.21,0:08:15.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.73,0:08:18.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.46,0:08:38.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你好
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.79,0:08:47.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是不是瘦了？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.82,0:08:49.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也许吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.16,0:08:52.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你受伤了？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.79,0:08:54.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在南边遇上了点事情
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.47,0:08:57.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没什么 擦伤而已
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.80,0:08:59.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.97,0:09:03.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,遇到艾尔利克兄弟了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.42,0:09:07.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说是去见达普利斯的师傅 偶然碰到了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.35,0:09:09.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,少佐
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.62,0:09:13.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你告诉他们休斯已经去世了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.24,0:09:17.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 没能说出口
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.62,0:09:20.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总有一天会知道的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.95,0:09:22.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.74,0:09:25.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,第五研究所和贤者之石
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.20,0:09:28.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,石头的材料是活生生的人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.87,0:09:31.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那家伙习惯管闲事
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.32,0:09:35.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,插手艾尔利克兄弟在调查的事件
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.56,0:09:38.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,知道了不应该知道的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.36,0:09:40.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.83,0:09:46.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为和自身的事件有关导致休斯死了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.40,0:09:49.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,两兄弟知道的话 心灵会受伤
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.74,0:09:52.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你真是个老好人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.24,0:09:55.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你调查得真彻底
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.04,0:09:57.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还差一把劲
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.85,0:10:00.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请小心
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.03,0:10:05.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说不定隔墙有耳
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.06,0:10:08.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么 我先走了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.19,0:10:18.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,霍克爱中尉？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.31,0:10:22.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好久不见
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.84,0:10:25.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,中尉在的话 也就是说…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.73,0:10:26.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让你久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.89,0:10:29.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.86,0:10:30.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,钢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.88,0:10:33.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么大佐会在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.62,0:10:36.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,上个月开始我转到中央工作了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.74,0:10:39.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,倒是你今天干什么来了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.60,0:10:43.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,稍微收集一下情报
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.27,0:10:47.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,另外想去和休斯中佐打声招呼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.56,0:10:49.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,中佐 还好吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.27,0:10:54.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不在了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.58,0:10:55.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.24,0:10:57.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他回乡下去了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.43,0:10:59.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,带着老婆和孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.32,0:11:02.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,准备继承家业
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.92,0:11:05.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以 不在了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.30,0:11:08.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗 真遗憾
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.03,0:11:10.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很想见他一面的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.49,0:11:15.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,钢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.95,0:11:19.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别因为太过于心急 而做鲁莽的事
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.85,0:11:36.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只在这种时候把他们当孩子吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.91,0:11:38.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们现在没有知道的必要
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.44,0:11:40.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对于那对兄弟来说
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.45,0:11:42.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,前进的路障
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.48,0:11:43.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还是越少越好
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.96,0:11:47.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 他们总有一天会知道
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.83,0:11:55.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也没资格说阿姆斯壮少佐是老好人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.60,0:11:59.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是一句老好人就能解决的事情吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.12,0:12:02.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太残酷了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.86,0:12:05.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,中佐不在了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.01,0:12:08.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对了 哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.33,0:12:10.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要快点通知温莉
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.44,0:12:11.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她已经去休斯家了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.43,0:12:13.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.69,0:12:18.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,罗斯少尉？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.11,0:12:20.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,两位好久不见了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.22,0:12:22.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了 这么急？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.05,0:12:25.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,听说了休斯中佐的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.54,0:12:29.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗 很痛苦吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.01,0:12:32.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有一堆话想和他说呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.73,0:12:34.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,至少想和他说声再见…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.78,0:12:37.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们没有收到通知呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.60,0:12:41.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没关系 全军都给他送行了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.21,0:12:44.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还挺人性化的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.87,0:12:46.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当然的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.88,0:12:49.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,另外 也许你们已经听说了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.52,0:12:53.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他晋升两级 不是中佐 是准将了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.41,0:12:55.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,晋升两级？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.35,0:12:58.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,回乡下了却能晋升两级？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.38,0:13:06.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,罗斯少尉？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.63,0:13:24.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,给 拿好
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.50,0:13:26.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.81,0:13:34.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不可能 为什么中佐会…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.51,0:13:35.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.94,0:13:43.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.83,0:13:49.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,休斯准将在爱德华出院后
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.85,0:13:51.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就被不明人物杀害了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.28,0:13:54.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,犯人还没被抓住
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.98,0:13:58.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是我的错
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.34,0:14:00.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是我把他卷进来了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.17,0:14:02.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,休斯中佐
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.18,0:14:18.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么 一路走好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.42,0:14:21.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下次再来中央都市的话 记得来打声招呼
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.18,0:14:25.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿尔冯斯穿着铠甲没法吃呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.38,0:14:28.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们还没决定住处吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.72,0:14:29.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么就来我家吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.36,0:14:49.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爸爸？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.43,0:15:08.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么办？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.21,0:15:10.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,实话实说
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.83,0:15:12.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.79,0:15:16.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,受责备的人只有我一个人就够了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.32,0:15:20.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这不是哥哥一个人的问题
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.40,0:15:21.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是我们两个人的问题
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.77,0:15:24.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以 我也去
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.41,0:15:28.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿尔 如果…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.62,0:15:32.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然决定了无论发生什么事都要取回身体
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.39,0:15:36.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果有人为此而死
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.14,0:15:38.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我宁愿放弃取回身体
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.13,0:15:47.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,温莉她…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.24,0:15:49.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.08,0:15:52.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,温莉
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.00,0:16:03.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我有话要对克蕾西亚夫人说
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.00,0:16:04.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.24,0:16:06.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对我说？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.45,0:16:07.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.31,0:16:09.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,温莉也来
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.30,0:16:18.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,丈夫知道了贤者之石的一些事
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.56,0:16:25.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我丈夫的死 是犯人警告你们不要再继续调查吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.87,0:16:30.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这完全是我们招来的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.61,0:16:31.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.80,0:16:37.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.42,0:16:44.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为了救人而死 真像那个人的作风
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.67,0:16:48.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从前就是个爱管闲事爱操心的人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.27,0:16:50.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老是帮了人家损了自己
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.26,0:16:55.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 我觉得他从来没有后悔过
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.45,0:16:59.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,即使在临死之时也是
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.73,0:17:01.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.75,0:17:05.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要说放弃之类的话
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.93,0:17:09.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果你们放弃了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.55,0:17:13.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我丈夫的死就会白费
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.84,0:17:17.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,即使贤者之石不行
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.84,0:17:19.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也许还有别的方法
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.34,0:17:24.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,克蕾西亚夫人…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.55,0:17:30.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请用自己可以接受的方式前进吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.13,0:17:37.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.05,0:17:40.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妈妈 别哭
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.96,0:18:42.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,温莉
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.97,0:18:43.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.46,0:18:49.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还没吃饭吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.63,0:18:52.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,食堂马上要关门了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.55,0:18:54.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.75,0:18:57.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不吃的话 身体会吃不消的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.44,0:18:59.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.07,0:19:03.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我回房间了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.45,0:19:09.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,苹果派？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.96,0:19:13.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从那之后 我练习了好多次
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.03,0:19:16.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,自己说出来像是自夸
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.05,0:19:18.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我已经能做得很好了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.91,0:19:22.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然比不上克蕾西亚夫人做的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.47,0:19:25.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总有一天
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.29,0:19:30.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也想让休斯先生尝尝的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.45,0:19:52.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大佐在调查休斯的事情？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.51,0:19:56.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抓住什么线索了？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.10,0:19:58.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也许吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.09,0:20:00.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么办？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.61,0:20:06.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为了方便监视 才把他调到了中央
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.00,0:20:09.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能不能让他乖乖待着
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.82,0:20:12.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他可是重要的人柱候补
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.70,0:20:15.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从你男朋友那里打听不出什么吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.73,0:20:16.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,完全没有
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.28,0:20:19.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真不知道他是天然呆还是老练
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.94,0:20:21.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我再去收集下情报
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.12,0:20:24.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,走了哦 库拉多尼
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.44,0:20:29.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 库拉多尼
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.15,0:20:31.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别吃完了不收拾
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.34,0:20:33.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.89,0:20:36.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我说 拉斯特
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.55,0:20:40.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要火焰之大佐安分下来就行了吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.74,0:20:46.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要试试另一个方法吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.49,0:20:49.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你有什么计策？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.73,0:20:54.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对于吵闹的狗 要给它点食物才行
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.42,0:21:00.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,玛丽亚·罗斯少尉
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.23,0:21:04.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是宪兵队司令部的 亨利·达古拉斯
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.59,0:21:07.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,找我有什么事
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.26,0:21:09.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,跟我们走一趟
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.44,0:21:11.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把枪交出来
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.98,0:21:17.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能说明一下吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.16,0:21:23.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们怀疑你杀害了马斯·休斯
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.46,0:21:25.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么可能
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.99,0:21:27.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等会听你的辩解
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.52,0:21:29.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,跟我们来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.99,0:21:36.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,玛丽亚·罗斯少尉否认罪行
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.53,0:21:39.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,收集这个人的相关资料
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.23,0:21:40.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,尽快
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.24,0:21:41.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.02,0:21:42.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要隐秘行动
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.19,0:21:43.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.85,0:21:55.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,婆婆 把这个花包一下
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.29,0:21:57.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,约会去吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.09,0:21:59.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你这个帅哥
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.70,0:22:15.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,久等了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.58,0:22:16.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,索拉莉丝
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.87,0:22:18.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.88,0:22:20.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,刚刚才到
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.58,0:22:22.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我好想你 约翰
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.16,0:22:25.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再说些有趣的故事给我听吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.64,0:24:03.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,替罪羔羊被仇恨之火焰所焚烧
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.92,0:24:07.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,少年受憎恶与后悔的侵蚀
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.46,0:24:09.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.40,0:24:12.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,男人把手伸向了黑暗
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.72,0:24:16.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下回 钢之炼金术师
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.22,0:24:17.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Fullmetal Alchemist
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.86,0:24:20.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,第17话 冰冷的火焰
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.64,0:24:25.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一切都如同在看不见的手上跳舞
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.03,0:00:00.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,【OP】
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.85,0:00:06.19,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,500)\blur4}纯白的景色在向我招手
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.22,0:00:12.71,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,1000)\blur4}我即将起程   前往那未知的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.46,0:00:21.68,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,0)\blur4}迷茫的旅途
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.71,0:00:24.46,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,0)\blur4}在灰色的天空下
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.49,0:00:30.54,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,0)\blur4}在不断变化的地图里 搀杂着各种梦想
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.54,0:00:32.93,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}总有一天
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.97,0:00:36.99,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,0)\blur4}即使以我这微小的步伐
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.06,0:00:43.05,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,0)\blur4}也能走到那云的彼端吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.05,0:00:44.68,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}故作坚强
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.68,0:00:46.22,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}却受了伤
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.28,0:00:49.30,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,0)\blur4}仿佛看透了一切
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.30,0:00:50.86,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}从天上落下的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.86,0:00:53.04,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}点点雨水
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.04,0:00:56.25,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}反复的漫反射
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.29,0:00:59.11,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,0)\blur4}笔直的光
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.11,0:01:01.83,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}相互交叉
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.89,0:01:05.42,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,0)\blur4}并不知道去向何方
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.42,0:01:06.71,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}只管
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.71,0:01:08.28,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}不停地前进
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.34,0:01:14.12,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,0)\blur4}淡淡的残影烙印在两眼中
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.12,0:01:16.05,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}在这片天空下
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.05,0:01:19.86,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,500)\blur4}无论身在何处
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.31,0:01:22.17,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,0)\blur4}一定可以到达
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.17,0:01:26.98,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,1000)\blur4}那未曾见过的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.03,0:00:00.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,【ED】
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.67,0:22:33.32,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,0)\fsp-1.5\fnRoman\fs35\b1}Let it all out, Let it all out
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.32,0:22:37.42,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,500)}不必故作坚强
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.68,0:22:44.20,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,有人这样描绘
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.20,0:22:50.00,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,在墙上涂鸦的花也会摇动
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.00,0:22:55.60,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,没人知道真正的自己
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.60,0:22:57.88,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,在漫长的路途中
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.88,0:23:01.30,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,失去与获取
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.30,0:23:08.99,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,500)}突然寂寞  也有哭泣的日子
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.07,0:23:16.48,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,眼泪也好  痛苦也好  都将化为恒星
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.48,0:23:22.49,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,点燃照亮明天的灯火
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.49,0:23:27.64,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,举起小手  两个人一起创造
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.64,0:23:32.85,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,去搜寻星尘与光芒四射的永远…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.85,0:23:38.22,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,再见 那天也许还会降临
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.22,0:23:44.16,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,500)}即使季节依然在不断地交替
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.47,0:23:48.24,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,就算有点迷茫  也要向前
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.24,0:23:52.28,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,与你一起前行
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.28,0:23:56.56,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,1000)}请让我维持到永远
